(13683, 'Alexadricaine 1:100000 - 50 cartridges 1.7 ml', 'اليكسادريكايين 1:100000 - 50 خرطوشة 1.7 مل', '540', '850', 'Articaine+adrinaline', 'Alexandria', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', 'مخدر موضعي -- مسكن للألم', 'Analgesic.local anesthetic', '1.7 ml', 'adrenaline : 0.017 mg articaine : 68 mg indication: an amide local anesthetic containing a vasoconstrictor is indicated for local infiltrative or conductive anesthesia in both simple and complex dental procedures. articaine hcl is an amide local anestheti', '', '', 1839, '2024-05-06', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(29183, 'Versapenia 50mg 30 f.c.tabs', 'فيرسابنيا 50مجم 30 قرص', '4017.75', '5,223', 'Eltrombopag olamine', 'Amoun', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'لعلاج نقص الصفائح الدموية', 'Thrombocytopenia', '50mg', 'Thrombopoietin receptor agonists are pharmaceutical agents that stimulate platelet production in the bone marrow. In this, they differ from the previously discussed agents that act by attempting to curtail platelet destruction.', '6221025047649', '', 18353, '2024-10-02', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
